name: Vuoto a perdere_02
description:
ioi_DgArt#001
"even today everything goes great"

" Vuoto a perdere "represents a critique of today's society, where appearance matters more than essence. The result is the need to always be perfect, approved, accepted. The risk is to denaturalize ourself and getting lost. Inside the sparkling shell only a bubble of emptiness remains.

4096x4096 px
